Pep Guardiola: &quot;Leroy San&eacute;? First impression was not good, but it's not bad. I spoke to the doctors but I don't know. We will wait but I think he will be ok.&quot; <br />
<br />
&quot;He came off because he was injured, it was scary. I was concerned about his injury. You believe I have a problem with him?..&quot;

Ilkay G&uuml;ndogan: &ldquo;I am very happy to have signed the new contract. I have hugely enjoyed the last three years here at City and everyone at the Club has helped make me feel at home from my very first day.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
&ldquo;It&rsquo;s a privilege to be a part of this team, playing the style of football we do and winning trophies. It's difficult to do that and I&rsquo;m delighted to be a part of it. I&rsquo;m really excited about what we can achieve in the next few seasons.&rdquo;
